A bold, (Expressionist:1.2) (masterpiece:1.15) of an individual, set against a dark 
or muted background. The subject should be rendered in rich, earthy tones 
of sienna red, umber brown, and moss green, with thick, impasto 
brushstrokes that capture the texture of skin and clothing.
Emphasize the expressive quality of the portrait, conveying a sense of 
personality and emotional depth through bold strokes and vivid color. 
Suggest the subtle play of light and shadow on the subject's face, but 
don't worry too much about precise detail  instead, focus on capturing 
the essence and character of the individual.
